WEBVTT

00:00:01.820 --> 00:00:07.506
Koinotdan-da ulkan va
yoshi ulug' narsa yo'q. [Stiven Hoking]

00:00:07.506 --> 00:00:13.358
Men bugun quyidagi savollar 
muhokamasiga to'xtalib o'tmoqchiman:

00:00:13.358 --> 00:00:17.840
birinchidan, bizning kelib chiqishimiz
qayerga borib taqaladi?

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:22.013
Koinot qanday paydo bo'lgan?
[2008-yil, fevral. Monterey, Kaliforniya]

00:00:22.013 --> 00:00:24.996
Biz koinotda yolg'izmizmi?

00:00:24.996 --> 00:00:28.144
O'zga sayyoralarda ham hayot mavjudmi?

00:00:28.144 --> 00:00:31.473
Insoniyatning kelajagi qanday?